    .govuk-grid-row
      .govuk-grid-column-two-thirds
        %h2.govuk-cookie-banner__heading.govuk-heading-m Cookies on Clean Air Zones
        .govuk-cookie-banner__content
          %p.govuk-body We use some essential cookies to make this website work.
